                    <div><input type="checkbox" id="q3" name="q3" /><label for="q3">Consider two sorting algorithms: Algorithm A with a time complexity of O(n log n) and Algorithm B with a time complexity of O(n^2). Under what conditions might you choose Algorithm B over Algorithm A?</label></div>
            </fieldset>
        </div>
        <input type="submit">
    </form>
</div>

